## 9.2 Wiring Plan
Describe the main electrical connections.

**Response:**  
`Each servo is powered from the breadboard power supply â€” red wire to 5V, brown/black wire to PS GND. The signal wire of servo 1 connects to ESP32 pin D13, and servo 2 to D27. Each roller lever switch has its COM terminal connected to ESP32 GND and its NO terminal connected to an ESP32 input pin â€” switch 1 to D4, switch 2 to D21. The ESP32 GND and breadboard power supply GND are bridged together with a single wire so all components share a common ground.`

