wait 0.5 seconds

last state of button1 = not pressed
last state of button2 = not pressed

loop forever:
    read current state of button1
    read current state of button2

    if button1 is now pressed and was not pressed before:
        move servo1 to 180 degrees
        wait 0.08 seconds
        move servo1 back to 0 degrees

    if button2 is now pressed and was not pressed before:
        move servo2 to 180 degrees
        wait 0.08 seconds
